Zendesk,is,a,software,as,a,service,company,that,provides,businesses,with,different,communication,tools,The,Zendesk,Core,API,enables,developers,to,integrate,the,Zendesk,platform,into,their,applications,With,this,API,users,of,the,applications,will,be,able,to,use,the,core,features,of,the,Zendesk,service,some,of,the,features,include,setting,limits,on,calls,automating,calls,access,to,call,records